==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|suprema}}

#{{mathematics}} (''of a subset'') the [[least]] [[element]] of the containing set that is [[greater]] or [[equal]] to all elements of the subset. The supremum may or may not be a member of the subset.

